    "description": "《朱鹭子的奇妙冒险》是以东方project为主题的二次创作游戏，是一款2D横版休闲向解谜游戏，玩家将会扮演在《东方project》中出场的“无名的读书妖怪”——一般被称为朱鹭子——运用各种魔法书的力量，解开谜题，解救他人，或是迎战强大的敌人，最终解决异变。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于故事</h2>朱鹭子在一次去红魔馆借阅图书的过程中，因为某些原因陷入昏迷，而在她苏醒之后，发现红魔馆的景色居然发生了变化，而且大家还被关在了笼子中无法动弹？！<br>抱着对现况的疑问，朱鹭子和红魔馆的小恶魔一起，踏上了救助红魔馆的大家的道路，而朱鹭子的故事也就此开始——<br><br><br><strong>在游戏中你可以看到：</strong><br><br>    <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可爱的朱鹭子</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188690/extras/bf7cebf30df08f40fe993ac367f4031c.poster.avif?t=1682784458\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188690/extras/bf7cebf30df08f40fe993ac367f4031c.webm?t=1682784458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>    <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可以和其他角色进行的互动</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188690/extras/ff0b744ba204513dfc01f701cdd76fbb.poster.avif?t=1682784458\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188690/extras/ff0b744ba204513dfc01f701cdd76fbb.webm?t=1682784458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188690/extras/ff0b744ba204513dfc01f701cdd76fbb.mp4?t=1682784458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>    <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基础机制：使用魔法书的力量！当然物理意义上的力量也包括在其中！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188690/extras/6a295e334b93c0184e954b4f56f4585a.poster.avif?t=1682784458\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188690/extras/6a295e334b93c0184e954b4f56f4585a.webm?t=1682784458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>    <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使用各种各样的魔法书的技能帮助自己</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188690/extras/e81b80fb476f26b0b3a8a593f74a94fd.poster.avif?t=1682784458\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188690/extras/e81b80fb476f26b0b3a8a593f74a94fd.webm?t=1682784458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188690/extras/e81b80fb476f26b0b3a8a593f74a94fd.mp4?t=1682784458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>    <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >乐子足够的剧情（确信）</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188690/extras/8fd929c32af066f8c012e8689a7e1f75.poster.avif?t=1682784458\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188690/extras/8fd929c32af066f8c012e8689a7e1f75.webm?t=1682784458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>    <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >见到幻想乡中数一数二的强者</h2>比如500岁的拥有强大实力的吸血鬼蕾米莉亚斯卡雷特<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188690/extras/40ff241a6d7315f6a2b578ff8a6b287c.poster.avif?t=1682784458\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188690/extras/40ff241a6d7315f6a2b578ff8a6b287c.webm?t=1682784458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>    <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与强敌展开战斗！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188690/extras/2d1a887495147682f145b37e2b284f25.poster.avif?t=1682784458\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188690/extras/2d1a887495147682f145b37e2b284f25.webm?t=1682784458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br><br>欢迎来体验朱鹭子的故事！<br><br>参与游戏讨论可以加入讨论QQ群：631707578",
